ACADEMIC INTEGRITY NOTICE:
This software was developed as part of an academic project at EPFL. If you are
a student taking the IAPR course or a similar computer vision course, please be
aware that submitting this work as your own may constitute academic dishonesty.
This code is made available for educational and research purposes. Students are
encouraged to understand the concepts and develop their own implementations.

DATASET NOTICE:
The chocolate dataset used in this project is property of the IAPR course at EPFL
and is used under academic license. The dataset should not be redistributed
without permission from the course instructors.

